  "title": "Incredibly Buttery Middle Eastern Lamb Shawarma",
  "description": "A light and flavorful Middle Eastern dish featuring tender lamb, crispy buttery bread, and fresh little gem lettuce, all wrapped up in a delicious shawarma.",
