  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the lamb slices onto skewers, if using, and season with sumac, garlic, salt, and pepper.",
    "Grill the lamb for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked to an internal temperature of 145 degrees.",
    "Warm the pita bread by wrapping it in foil and heating it in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "Spread a layer of tahini sauce on each pita bread.",
    "Assemble the shawarma by placing a few slices of the grilled lamb onto each pita bread, followed by a spoonful of melted butter, a few leaves of little gem lettuce, and a sprinkle of sumac.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Repeat with the remaining ingredients.",
    "Let the shawarma rest for a few minutes before serving to allow the flavors to meld together."
